title: Starbucks to sell rights to Nestle
text:
Starbucks to sell rights to Nestle 9:25pm BST - 01:28
Starbucks said it will sell the rights for some of its products around the world to Swiss-based food giant Nestle for $7.15 billion in cash. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
